ge(`\\\"` + agents.DefaultDroidModel() + `\\\"`)\\n\\n// After:\\nmodelJSON, err := json.Marshal(agents.DefaultDroidModel())\\nif err != nil {\\n    return fmt.Errorf(\\\"marshal model setting: %w\\\", err)\\n}\\nrepoSettings[\\\"model\\\"] = json.RawMessage(modelJSON)\\n```\\n\\n### 2. `e2e/agents/tmux.go:162-169` — Treat tmux errors as dead pane\\n**Problem:** `IsPaneDead()` returns `false` on tmux errors (e.g., session not found), causing `WaitFor` to poll the full timeout on a nonexistent pane.\\n**Fix:** When tmux command fails, check if the error output indicates the session/pane no longer exists and treat that as dead.\\n\\n**File:** `e2e/agents/tmux.go:162-169`\\n\\n### 3. `e2e/agents/droid.go:202` — Make sleep context-aware\\n**Problem:** `time.Sleep(2 * time.Second)` ignores context cancellation/deadlines.\\n**Fix:** Replace with timer + select on `ctx.Done()`.\\n\\n**File:** `e2e/agents/droid.go:200-203`\\n\\n## Verification\\n```bash\\nmise run fmt && mise run lint && mise run test:ci\\n```\\n\"}\n{\"parentUuid\":\"b6beecd3-4454-4a0a-a97c-d1028d63154f\",\"isSidechain\":false,\"userType\":\"external\",\"cwd\":\"/Users/alisha/Projects/wt/droid-e2e-ci\",\"sessionId\":\"46c118bb-d5d8-4454-97cd-cd36a6be1955\",\"version\":\"2.1.68\",\"gitBranch\":\"alisha/droid-e2e-ci\",\"slug\":\"partitioned-sleeping-valiant\",\"message\":{\"model\":\"claude-opus-4-6\",\"id\":\"msg_017CPEM56wvW7zoYTbGT4LCQ\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"\\n\\n`★ Insight ─────────────────────────────────────`\\nThese three fixes address common robustness patterns in E2E test infrastructure:\\n1. **JSON injection safety** — string concatenation for JSON is fragile; `json.Marshal` handles escaping\\n2. **Error semantics** — when checking external process state, command failure often means \\\"gone\\\", not \\\"unknown\\\"\\n3. **Context-aware delays** — `time.Sleep` is a concurrency anti-pattern in Go; `select` on `ctx.Done()` enables can